{"tid":244801,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖] 貓仔隻手紅左一撻","createTime":"2017-05-15T16:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-15T18:58:27.000Z","uid":59261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"94bc470075e8175095901860ea5c6598dd0b4a43","tid":244801,"uid":59261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T16:59:01.000Z","msg":"借朋友account 出post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身細細忽, 少少粉紅, 以為淨係少少甩毛<br />\n今晚一睇!! 大左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋佢甩多左毛<br />\n嗚呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/005434_fcdaced801ac182e31ee2c25873d883f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F005434_fcdaced801ac182e31ee2c25873d883f.jpg&h=87c8dd4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人試過或者知道會係咩原因 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會盡快帶佢睇醫生<br />\n順便問埋住九龍灣, 附近會唔會有好既獸醫 / 診所 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89449bb65e5dc8915af08a62a2601bf7435c1000","tid":244801,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T17:00:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"edc19e79efee838c9a1f9cb414fa7071cd6f7d06","tid":244801,"uid":55469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T17:00:49.000Z","msg":"係咪貓貓咬手？之前養狗都有試過<br />\n之後睇獸醫俾藥糕佢搽就無事啦！"},{"pid":"6a2dd39f23ebdf0b78d38b2ba3919acd644121b6","tid":244801,"uid":17904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T17:00:50.000Z","msg":"點睇都似係割/𠝹到無左忽肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未緊急到要即刻睇醫生嘅，訓醒帶佢去啦"},{"pi