al/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又驚佢係咁想整甩嗰陣又會整到隻手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c22dd7b72a0fdd37ac0f5226a7f6d80c20c21669","tid":244801,"uid":59261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T18:58:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽日帶佢睇獸醫啦，應該細菌感染</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  希望佢會乖乖地唔好再搞 / lam"}]}